sentences: Born and raised in Buffalo, New York, Steven began his career in the music industry managing his friends' bands, eventually founding his company in 2012.

section: == Early life and career == | === 1992–2011: early life ===

sentences: In 2012, Steven met Evan Baker of The Analog Affair and officially founded his artist management company.
In 2013, Steven signed Los Angeles band Street Joy and Brooklyn band Wildlife Control (band) to his management roster.
In 2011, Steven moved from Buffalo, New York to Gainesville, Florida.
He currently lives in Tampa, Florida.
